com.CMPUT301W15T02.teamtoapp.Model

Class Claim

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.CMPUT301W15T02.teamtoapp.Model.Claim
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Listener

    public class Claim
extends java.lang.Object
implements Listener
    Stores all of the data related to a claim including any associated expenses. Claim watches its expenses and must be updated when an expense updates.
    Author:
    Kyle Carlstrom, Raman Dhatt
